  "detailed_description": "'Elon Simulator' is an immersive 'Trillionaire Simulator' with dozens of fun mechanics and activities to engage in!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe year is 2030, and the Earth is starved for Lithium. <br />\r\nGood thing you have an ample supply of it, right outside your Private Luxury Space-Station!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAs Elon, you can:<br />\r\n     Smoke Weed (a lot)<br />\r\n     Print your own money<br />\r\n     Purchase and Create Corporations<br />\r\n     Blow your money on expensive toys<br />\r\n     Explore space in your 'Iron Billionaire' Suit<br />\r\n     Go 'Lithium Hunting' in your Flying SpaceCar (Then sell the lithium back to Earth for BILLIONS $$$)<br />\r\n     Make MILLIONS while you sleep in real life...<br />\r\n     Play on the Holo-Table<br />\r\n     Become a TRILLIONAIRE<br />\r\n     ...and lots more....<br />\r\n<br />\r\n     All from the comfort of your gigantic Luxury Space station, which is headed to Mars for permanent residence!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou are Elon: the richest man in the Galaxy. And you can afford anything you want.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nI made this game as a skills test and to pad my portfolio for future employers to see... and also to let people have fun in deep space with unlimited earning potential. Have fun!",
  "about_the_game": "'Elon Simulator' is an immersive 'Trillionaire Simulator' with dozens of fun mechanics and activities to engage in!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe year is 2030, and the Earth is starved for Lithium. <br />\r\nGood thing you have an ample supply of it, right outside your Private Luxury Space-Station!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAs Elon, you can:<br />\r\n     Smoke Weed (a lot)<br />\r\n     Print your own money<br />\r\n     Purchase and Create Corporations<br />\r\n     Blow your money on expensive toys<br />\r\n     Explore space in your 'Iron Billionaire' Suit<br />\r\n     Go 'Lithium Hunting' in your Flying SpaceCar (Then sell the lithium back to Earth for BILLIONS $$$)<br />\r\n     Make MILLIONS while you sleep in real life...<br />\r\n     Play on the Holo-Table<br />\r\n     Become a TRILLIONAIRE<br />\r\n     ...and lots more....<br />\r\n<br />\r\n     All from the comfort of your gigantic Luxury Space station, which is headed to Mars for permanent residence!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou are Elon: the richest man in the Galaxy. And you can afford anything you want.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nI made this game as a skills test and to pad my portfolio for future employers to see... and also to let people have fun in deep space with unlimited earning potential. Have fun!",
